CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

September 8, 2006

[Cite as 09/08/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-4591.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2006-1211. Allianz Global Risks US Ins. Co. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, Nos. 05-1011-EL-CSS and 05-1012-EL-CSS. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
